ronment. This is a challenge for the inorganic chemist and also, most\nnotably, for the theoretical and the computational chemist. This chapter gives\nan overview of the issues tied to the application of DFT and TD-DFT to the\ncharacterisation of transition metal complexes in the framework of\nspin-crossover and related phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2012 20:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 15:13:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-24"}
