 single-photon\napplications where ultra-low noise and free-running operation is required, and\nsome afterpulsing can be tolerated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2012 22:01:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 20:54:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 31 May 2012 21:22:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-18"}
